| Non-stick surface | [link](http://localhost:8090/content/wikipedia_en_all_nopic/Non-stick_surface) | A non-stick surface is a surface engineered to reduce the ability of other materials to stick to it, commonly used in cookware as a coating such as PTFE (Teflon) or ceramic. |
